19 YATICHÄWI ¿Khitis Amuyasiri Cheqapa Uywatajja? Jiwañapajj jakʼankjjäna ukhaw Jesusajj pusi arkirinakapamp tantachasïna: Pedro, Santiago (jan ukajj Jacobo), Juan ukhamarak Andrés. Ukatsti, jupajj kuttʼankani ukat akapachajj tukuskani ukhajj kunanakas pasañapäna uka toqenakat qhanañchkasajja, akham sasaw arkirinakapar jisktʼäna: “¿Khitiraki amuyasiri, cheqap uywatasti, khitirutï uywiripajj utapankirinakjjaru uchawayi, horasaparu manqʼa jupanakaru churañapatakejja?” sasa (Mateo 24:3; 24:45, MT; 
..........
uywataw Diosan utap uñji (1 Timoteo 3:15). ‘Amuyasiri Cheqapa Uywatajj’ aka Oraqenkiri Jehová Diosan markap uñjañatak uttʼayatäpjjewa, Jesusaw uka luräwi jaytawayi, ukatwa Diosan markapan utjir yänakap uñjapjje, Diosan arunakapat yatiyasiñapatak yanaptʼapjje ukat tamanak taypis yatichapjjaraki. Janiw ukakïkiti, Diosan yupaychirinakapar kunanakatï wakisi ukanak horasapar churañatakejja, Diosan arunakap yatiyañataki apnaqaski uka Bibliat apstʼat qellqatanakampisa ukat kunanakatï tantachäwinakansa,
